        "uid": "99833"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t最近在看基于ipfs的聊天系统的一些东西<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9kb2NzLmlwZnMudGVjaC9ob3ctdG8vY3JlYXRlLXNpbXBsZS1jaGF0LWFwcC8jaG93LWl0LXdvcmtz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://docs.ipfs.tech/how-to/create-simple-chat-app/#how-it-works\">https://docs.ipfs.tech/how-to/create-simple-chat-app/#how-it-works</a><br/>\n<br/>\n另，楼主可以在3DES的基础上加上Diffie-Hellman Key Exchange 来建立私钥。用时间做密钥太容易被搞了。楼主可以看看 Double Ratchet Algorithm，大体上是 Diffie-Hellman + MAC + AES. Signal和WhatsApp 好像用的都是这个算法。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-12-04",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 1,
      "discussions": [
        {
          "id": "1132336",
          "replier": {
